    <!-- Help -->
    <string name="help_title">IntelliHome Registration Guide</string>

    <string name="help_content">
        Follow these steps to create your account correctly:\n\n
        1. **Basic Info:** Enter your first name, last name, and a valid email address.\n\n
        2. **Profile Picture:** You must select a photo. Ensure it is smaller than 1MB.\n\n
        3. **Security:** Create a unique username and a strong password. Avoid using offensive language.\n\n
        4. **Biometrics:** If your phone supports it, enable fingerprint login for faster access.\n\n
        5. **Recovery:** Select a security question. This will be the only way to recover your account if you forget your password.\n\n
        6. **Preferences:** You must select your housing types and at least one hobby to personalize your smart home experience.\n\n
        7. **Payment Method:** Register your card for automatic service management.
    </string>
